    <item>
      <title>阿根廷人对米莱伊经济越来越乐观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/argentines-are-increasingly-positive-about-the-milei-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷人对该国陷入困境的经济的未来变得更加乐观，这一转变将在今年晚些时候的中期选举之前鼓舞主张紧缩政策的总统哈维尔·米莱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/argentines-are-increasingly-positive-about-the-milei-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥民众谴责犯罪和腐败，谢恩鲍姆支持率下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/sheinbaum-s-support-slips-as-mexicans-decry-crime-and-corruption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项最新民意调查显示，由于选民强烈要求墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·希因鲍姆采取更强有力的打击犯罪和腐败的行动，其支持率在其执政约 100 天后下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/sheinbaum-s-support-slips-as-mexicans-decry-crime-and-corruption</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
